ygData.messageBody:
Do you mean Ykesha, as in Dulak, Gunthak, etc.? Have you tried
http://www.mapfiend.net/, they have maps for the automap function and
pdf files to download. They are a great help.

EQ Atlas stopped posting maps and guides when Sony came our with
their own atlas. He got discouraged after that. He still posts
other peoples maps as they are submitted.

Tuldayen Grimblade
Outrider of Tunare
